it enables you to visually separate

00:37:50.610 --> 00:37:52.920
these related lists of content.

00:37:52.920 --> 00:37:55.940
And you'll see,
as you mock up your own applications,

00:37:55.940 --> 00:37:59.900
notice that the playlist applications
that Apple has are using Metal,

00:37:59.900 --> 00:38:01.390
and there's very good reason there.

00:38:01.400 --> 00:38:04.040
Hopefully you'll also notice
as you install Panther that

00:38:04.040 --> 00:38:07.240
there's a lot more consistency in
